司”和“俄罗斯天然气工业银行”列入其中，匈牙利将不会支持，因为这会导致匈牙利天然气供应的中断。 罗马尼亚副总理：欧盟今冬将付出代价 同一天，罗马尼亚副总理凯莱门·胡诺尔在接受当地电视台采访时也表示，“今年冬天，欧盟将为制裁俄罗斯付出代价”。他警告说，对于整个欧洲来说，今年冬天可能将是过去几十年来最寒冷的一个冬天。欧盟拟对俄罗斯实施第七轮制裁 多国担忧新制裁加剧能源危机"},"attached_info":"Cj4I8NGc4Mjq+IBiEAMaCDgzMDM1ODc4IIGJw5YGMAA4P0Abcgk1NDMzOTA2NDJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"75 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-6e75955d9f69f1f30f6a5340b7799011_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1658142679.761253","card_id":"Q_285730093","target":{"id":285730093,"title":"有哪些值得计算机专业学生加入的国企？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/285730093","type":"question","created":1531879268,"answer_count":22,"follower_count":1408,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[99,6391,13306,16736],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"普通985计算机专业研一，开学就研二了，离找工作也不远了。师兄师姐基本都是去了互联网公司，缺少了解国企的信息渠道。想请教一下有经验的前辈，对于计算机研究生来说有哪些不错的国企可以考虑，方便的话说一下各方面的情况：待遇，加班情况，晋升情况，工作氛围等。(研究所，央企，银行有编制的都可以)"},"attached_info":"Cj8I8NGc4Mjq+IBiEAMaCDI1NzcyODI2IOS+utoFMAA4gAtAHHIJMjg1NzMwMDkzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"70 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-51966090eedd0dcbae32023a02625a9e_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"29_1658142679.7618895","card_id":"Q_543642160","target":{"id":543642160,"title":"天赋真的比努力更有用吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/543642160","type":"question","created":1657963904,"answer_count":106,"follower_count":112,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[6659,8198,9522],"comment_count":2,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4I8NGc4Mjq+IBiEAMaCDgzMDkxOTIyIICLypYGMAI4cEAdcgk1NDM2NDIxNjB4AKoB